  "description": "Describes the government’s strategic vision for the railways, and the actions we are taking to make it a reality.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This document outlines the government’s strategic vision for the railways and explains what we are doing to make it a reality.</p>\n\n<p>It explains our plans to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>bring the organisations that run the track and the trains closer together to deliver better services for passengers</li>\n  <li>invest in upgrades to the network to deliver faster journey times, more capacity, and support economic growth</li>\n  <li>improve the customer experience, including provision for smart ticketing</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
